<div class="linkdiv "><a class="linkdiv" href="bluetooth-remove-connection.html.ca" title="Disconnect a Bluetooth device"><span class="title">Disconnect a Bluetooth device</span><span class="linkdiv-dash"> — </span><span class="desc">Com esborrar un dispositiu de la llista de dispositius Bluetooth.</span></a></div>
